      <title>中国考虑允许对 5.4 万亿美元的抵押贷款进行再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-mulls-allowing-refinancing-on-5-4-trillion-in-mortgages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正考虑允许房主对高达 5.4 万亿美元的抵押贷款进行再融资，以降低数百万家庭的借贷成本并刺激消费。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-mulls-allowing-refinancing-on-5-4-trillion-in-mortgages</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:50:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
